# Go API

- **Canonical tree:** `apps/template/go-api` (or `apps/<slug>/go-api`). Handlers `internals/transport/http/handlers/<domain>/`, services `internals/services/<domain>/`, repos `internals/repositories/<domain>/`.
- **Shared lib:** `github.com/yca-software/go-common` via `replace` in app `go.mod` → `../../../packages/go-common`.
- **Wiring:** new domains → `repositories.go`, `internals/services/services.go`, `internals/transport/http/gateway.go`, and Swagger on handlers.
- **Schema:** SQL only in `migrations/`. **Docs:** `make swagger` updates `docs/swagger.json` / `docs/swagger.yaml`.
- **Validate:** from API dir: `make test`; after repo/migration changes: `make test-integration`. See `Makefile` targets.
